        "Product_Description": "Explore the neighborhood, head to the park, or enjoy family outings with the Baby Trend Expedition 2-in-1 Stroller Wagon. This stroller wagon converts between push stroller mode and pull wagon mode, giving you flexible use for walks, outdoor events, and travel. It also offers a car seat adapter option for infant carrier seats, making it useful from the early months through the toddler years. Inside, the extra-large main compartment provides room for 2 children with built-in cushioned seats and 3-point safety harnesses. Each seat accommodates children up to 55 pounds. When extra lounging space is needed, the seat cushions can be unfolded into a nap pad for rest time or quick diaper changes while away from home. Storage is built into the design to keep essentials close at hand. A flip-over basket can be attached to the front or back of the wagon, while a removable center snack console with 2 cup holders fits between the child seats for drinks and snacks. Extra storage helps keep diaper bags, bottles, and travel items more organized during outings. The 2-In-1 Stroller Wagon folds into a compact design for easier storage and transport. One-touch removable wheels help save space in the car or at home. With room for 2 children, push and pull functionality, and built-in storage, this stroller wagon is ready for family use.",
